	(116, 1, 50, 3, 0, 'o', 'Puma Nuna', 'pneves@outlook.com', '', '', '127.0.0.1', 1413448260, NULL, 'Also, be great if you can save the results into something like memcache so more then one server can access the cache'),
	(117, 1, 50, 3, 0, 'o', 'Greg Wineman', 'greg@ambidustrio.us', '', '', '127.0.0.1', 1413242520, NULL, 'I\'m wondering if the capability to combine share counts was ever implemented. Also, do the results cache so we aren\'t hitting the services every time the plugin is called?'),
	(118, 1, 50, 3, 0, 'o', 'bhashkar007', 'bhashkar007@gmail.com', '', '', '127.0.0.1', 1413242880, NULL, 'Hi Greg,\n\n\nYes, I am about the launch the new version of this add-on which will have some additional features including combined total share count, caching, CRON etc.\n\n\nThe new version might be available soon or till next week.\n\n\nThanks'),
