	(12, 1, 4, 'ui-ux-graphic-design', 'webpage', '{layout=\"_layout/default\"}\n<div role=\"main\" class=\"main\">\n	<section class=\"page-header page-header-classic page-header-md\">\n		<div class=\"container\">\n			<div class=\"row\">\n				<div class=\"col-md-8 order-2 order-md-1 align-self-center p-static\">\n					<h1 data-title-border>UI / UX / Graphic Design</h1>\n				</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n	</section>\n\n\n	<div class=\"container pb-1\">\n		<div class=\"row\">\n			<div class=\"col-lg-10\">\n				<div class=\"overflow-hidden\">\n					<p class=\"lead mb-1 appear-animation\" data-appear-animation=\"maskUp\" data-appear-animation-delay=\"200\">\n						360Adaptive has designing experts who understand that design is not only design but a patent of various psychological facts put into a structure regardless of the name of structure - a webpage, app, logo or even an icon.\n					</p>\n					<p class=\"lead mb-0 appear-animation\" data-appear-animation=\"maskUp\" data-appear-animation-delay=\"500\">\n						Business websites need a creative User Interface to provide delightful user experiences. A visually appealing storefront design targets the visitors and they return to become your potential long-term customers. Research says, among millions of websites, people like to revisit handful ones who give them a visual delight while visiting. Users love a website that is good to see, easy to use and simple to extract information as they need.\n						<br />\n						<strong>We provide a wide range of exclusive UI / UX / Graphics Design services to the businesses.</strong>\n					</p>					\n				</div>\n			</div>\n			<div class=\"col-lg-2 appear-animation\" data-appear-animation=\"fadeIn\" data-appear-animation-delay=\"800\">\n				<a href=\"{path=\'get-a-quote\'}\" class=\"btn btn-primary font-weight-semibold text-3 px-5 btn-py-2\">Get a Quote!</a>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n\n	<section class=\"section bg-color-grey section-height-3 border-0 mt-5 mb-0\">\n		<div class=\"conta