	(22, 1, 4, 'expressionengine-cartthrob-development', 'webpage', '{layout=\"_layout/default\"}\n<div role=\"main\" class=\"main\">\n	<section class=\"page-header page-header-classic page-header-md\">\n		<div class=\"container\">\n			<div class=\"row\">\n				<div class=\"col-md-8 order-2 order-md-1 align-self-center p-static\">\n					<h1 data-title-border>ExpressionEngine + CartThrob Development</h1>\n				</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n	</section>\n\n	<div class=\"container pb-1 mb-4\">\n		<div class=\"row\">\n			<div class=\"col-lg-10\">\n				<div class=\"overflow-hidden\">\n					<p class=\"lead mb-1\">\n						Cartthrob is one of the most powerful ExpressionEngine e-commerce shopping cart frameworks. It is a highly efficient tool or a collection of tools that helps to build e-commerce sites that suits your specific business requirement. With the introduction of CartThrob 4, it has become more powerful and robust framework for developing e-commerce websites. It also has the powerful features of the ExpressionEngine framework, which makes it the right choice for building efficient and cost-effective e- commerce websites you need to build your online presence solid.\n					</p>\n				</div>\n			</div>\n			<div class=\"col-lg-2 appear-animation\" data-appear-animation=\"fadeIn\" data-appear-animation-delay=\"800\">\n				<a href=\"{path=\'get-a-quote\'}\" class=\"btn btn-primary font-weight-semibold text-3 px-5 btn-py-2\">Get a Quote!</a>\n			</div>\n		</div>	\n	</div>\n\n	<hr class=\"solid my-5\">\n\n	<div class=\"container\">\n		<div class=\"row\">\n			<div class=\"col\">\n				<h2 class=\"font-weight-normal text-7 mb-2\">Why <strong class=\"font-weight-extra-bold\">CartThrob?</strong></h2>\n				<p class=\"lead\">CartThrob is a powerful e-commerce extension for Expressions Engine Framework, which can be used for making applications beyond the e-commerce development. You can build flexible and scalable e-commerce solutions with the help of CartThrob and ExpressionEngine. With these powerful tools, you can expect –</p>\n				<div class=\"toggle toggle-primary\" data-plugin-toggle>\n					<section class=\"toggle active\">\n						<label>Development beyond limits</label>\n						<p>You can develop your online store as you want beyond limits with CartThrob and the flexible ExpressionEngine. You can improve your user experiences and grow your sales by using powerful features like customer accounts, product search, order history, shipping status, gift cards, shipping options, promotion codes, and wish lists.</p>\n					</section>\n					<section class=\"toggle\">\n						<label>Highly optimized store</label>\n						<p>You can create a highly optimized online shop that actually helps you grow your sales and online customer base. With CartThrob and ExpressionEngine, we develop search engine optimized codes that help you get higher rank in different search engines. Our CartThrob developers help to make your websites more crawlable and reachable by the search engines as well as compelling for the visitors.</p>\n					</section>\n					<section class=\"toggle\">\n						<label>Secure approach</label>\n						<p>With CartThrob and ExpressionEngine you can use industry’s best security approach and SSL layers for your application as you like.</p>\n					</section>\n					<section class=\"toggle\">\n						<label>Mobile friendly designs</label>\n						<p>CartThrob with ExpressionEngine offers the flexibility to design and develop your website making it mobile friendly that helps your online presence even more solid.</p>\n					</section>\n				</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n\n\n	<section class=\"call-to-action call-to-action-primary mb-5\">\n		<div class=\"container\">\n			<div class=\"row\">\n				<div class=\"col-sm-9 col-lg-9\">\n					<div class=\"call-to-action-content\">\n						<h3>Having a project in mind?</h3>\n						<p class=\"mb-0\">Develop flexible, scalable and secure e-commerce solutions with 360Adaptive CartThrob and ExpressionEngine e-commerce development services and stay ahead in the competition.</p>\n					</div>\n				</div>\n				<div class=\"col-sm-3 col-lg-3\">\n					<div class=\"call-to-action-btn\">\n						<a href=\"{path=\'contact-us\'}\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"btn btn-modern text-2 btn-light border-0\">Contact Us Now</a>\n					</div>\n				</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n	</section>\n\n	<section class=\"section bg-color-grey section-height-3 border-0 mt-5 mb-0\">\n		<div class=\"container\">\n\n			<div class=\"row\">\n				<div class=\"col\">\n\n					<div class=\"row align-items-center pt-4 appear-animation\" data-appear-animation=\"fadeInLeftShorter\">\n						<div class=\"col-md-4 mb-4 mb-md-0\">\n							<img class=\"img-fluid scale-2 pr-5 pr-md-0 my-4\" src=\"/assets/img/layout-styles.png\" alt=\"layout styles\" />\n						</div>\n						<div class=\"col-md-8 pl-md-5\">\n							<h2 class=\"font-weight-normal text-6 mb-3\"><strong class=\"font-weight-extra-bold\">CartThrob Development</strong> services we provide</h2>\n							<p>We at 360 Adaptive develop and design ExpressionEngine e-commerce applications for diverse business verticals for industries like healthcare, fashion, retail and more. CartThrob Development Services we provide include –</p>\n							<ul class=\"list list-icons list-icons-style-2\">\n								<li><i class=\"fas fa-check\"></i> Custom CartThrob E-commerce Development</li>\n								<li><i class=\"fas fa-check\"></i> CartThrob Migration and Upgradation</li>\n								<li><i class=\"fas fa-check\"></i> CartThrob Integration Services</li>\n								<li><i class=\"fas fa-check\"></i> CartThrob Custom Tools Development</li>\n								<li><i class=\"fas fa-check\"></i> Add-on and Plugin Development</li>\n								<li><i class=\"fas fa-check\"></i> CartThrob Support and Maintenance</li>\n							</ul>\n							<a class=\"mb-1 mt-1 mr-1 btn btn-primary\" href=\"{path=\'contact-us\'}\">Share your requirements with us <i class=\"fas fa-arrow-right ml-1\"></i> </a>\n						</div>\n					</div>\n\n					<hr class=\"solid my-5\">\n\n					<div class=\"row align-items-center pt-5 pb-3 appear-animation\" data-appear-animation=\"fadeInRightShorter\">\n						<div class=\"col-md-8 pr-md-5 mb-5 mb-md-0\">\n							<h2 class=\"font-weight-normal text-6 mb-3\">Why 360Adaptive Technologies?</h2>\n							<ul class=\"list list-icons list-icons-style-2\">\n								<li><i class=\"fas fa-check\"></i> Experienced CartThrob and ExpressionEngine Developers that build e-commerce applications which actually work.</li>\n								<li><i class=\"fas fa-check\"></i> Dedicated team to provide SEO friendly and optimized website development services</li>\n								<li><i class=\"fas fa-check\"></i> Comprehensive testing of quality at every stage of application development to ensure 100% quality before delivering it to the client.</li>\n								<li><i class=\"fas fa-check\"></i> Comprehensive analysis of your specific business requirements, business goals, and existing business processes before the design and development stage to provide a unique solution for your e-commerce business.</li>\n								<li><i class=\"fas fa-check\"></i> We provide transparency in communication throughout the development cycles and processes.</li>\n								<li><i class=\"fas fa-check\"></i> Faster turn-around time for completion of the project.</li>\n								<li><i class=\"fas fa-check\"></i> Cost effective solutions for competitive prices</li>\n								<li><i class=\"fas fa-check\"></i> 24*7 online support</li>\n							</ul>\n						</div>\n						<div class=\"col-md-4 px-5 px-md-3\">\n							<img class=\"img-fluid scale-2 my-4\" src=\"/assets/img/style-switcher.png\" alt=\"style switcher\" />\n						</div>\n					</div>\n\n				</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n	</section>\n\n</div>', NULL, 1551008842, 1, 'n', 0, '', 'n', 'n', 'o', 0, 'n'),
	(23, 1, 4, 'wordpress-woocommerce-development', 'webpage', '{layout=\"_layout/default\"}\n<div role=\"main\" class=\"main\">\n	<section class=\"page-header page-header-classic page-header-md\">\n		<div class=\"container\">\n			<div class=\"row\">\n				<div class=\"col-md-8 order-2 order-md-1 align-self-center p-static\">\n					<h1 data-title-border>WordPress + WooCommerce Development</h1>\n				</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n	</section>\n\n\n	<div class=\"container pb-1\">\n		<div class=\"row\">\n			<div class=\"col-lg-10\">\n				<div class=\"overflow-hidden\">\n					<p class=\"lead mb-1\">\n						The team of professionals at 360Adaptive Technologies has expertise in building e-commerce stores with excellent design and robust architecture. Every successful eCommerce business is the result of designing with keeping strategy in mind. Our experts understand your business requirements in depth and do a thorough analysis of the market and current development trends. As a WooCommerce Development Company, we provide practical and error-free enterprise-ready solutions for your specific business requirements.\n					</p>\n				</div>\n			</div>\n			<div class=\"col-lg-2 appear-animation\" data-appear-animation=\"fadeIn\" data-appear-animation-delay=\"800\">\n				<a href=\"{path=\'get-a-quote\'}\" class=\"btn btn-primary font-weight-semibold text-3 px-5 btn-py-2\">Get a Quote!</a>\n			</div>\n		</div>	\n\n		<div class=\"row\">\n			<div class=\"col py-3\">\n				<hr class=\"solid mt-0 mb-0\">\n			</div>\n		</div>\n\n\n		<div class=\"row\">\n			<div class=\"col-lg-12\">\n				<div class=\"overflow-hidden text-center\">\n					<h3 class=\"mb-2 mt-2 font-weight-normal\">Why should you choose <strong class=\"font-weight-extra-bold\">WooCommerce Development</strong> for your online store?</div>\n					<p class=\"mb-2 mt-2 text-center\">WooCommerce is an eCommerce plugin for WordPress. It is rich in features like inventory and tax management and secures payments. It is also best for shippin